	<td bgcolor="#F7F7F7" width="100%" valign="top">
	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial"><img src="../ubb/icons/icon1.gif" alt="Post" border="0"> <b>Your class balancing ideas for clerics!</b></font>
	<p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Please feel free to post your cleric class balancing ideas here.  Thinking outside of the box is welcome and encouraged. <br />
<br />
A few rules.....<br />
<br />
1) <b> <u> No Trolling Allowed. </b> </u><br />
<br />
2) <b> <u> No feeding trolls </b> </u>  <br />
<br />
In the event rule #1 is broken.  I will do my best to advise moderators of trollish posts and have them removed.<br />
<br />
3) <b> <u> No flaming. </b> </u> <br />
<br />
If you disagree with a post start a thread in rants, private message or voice your objection civilly in a new thread of your creation.<br />
<br />
I will be updating a list of ideas that clerics agree on, under this post.<br />
<br />
                    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />
<br />
<b> <u> Cleric Ideas </b> </u><br />
<br />
<b> Voted #1 </b> <br />
True plate class Damage Mitigation &#123; 25 Votes } <br />
<br />
#2<br />
Raise dodge cap  &#123; 16 Votes }<br />
<br />
#3<br />
Deity Specific spells &#123; 12 Votes } <br />
<br />
#4 - #7 Tied &#123; 11 Votes Each }<br />
Self Invis<br />
<br />
Group resist buffs<br />
<br />
Expand MoK / MoR line<br />
<br />
More undead zones<br />
<br />
#8 - # 10 Tied &#123; 10 Votes Each }<br />
Upgrade MoR <br />
<br />
Better undead dots <br />
<br />
Bless spells</font></p>
	
	<p><p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">__________________<br>
Soulforger Mountcalm <br />
62 Merchant Cleric of Brell <br />
<br />
Master of all tradeskills 150+ and 235 Skill Blacksmith<br />
