<table bgcolor="#FFFFFF" width="95%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr><td width="10"><img width="10" height="1" src="images/space.gif" alt=""></td><td width="100%"><!-- spacer -->

<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" bgcolor=""  width="95%" align="center"><tr><td>
<table cellpadding="4" cellspacing="1" border="0"  width="100%">
<tr>
	<td bgcolor="#F7F7F7" width="175" valign="top" nowrap>
	<a name="post120734"></a>
	
	<font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>Rollie</b></font><br>
	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">Level 57 forever!</font><br>
	<p>
	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">Registered: Feb 2002<br>
	Location: Wisconsin, the cold part.<br>
	Posts: 70</font></td>
	
	<td bgcolor="#F7F7F7" width="100%" valign="top">
	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial"> <b></b></font>
	<p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I saw a good idea on a different thread about a spell that we could cast to 'imbue' a proc on people's weapons (a 'prayer', so to speak).   To expand on this idea:<br />
<br />
1) Prayer cannot be cast on your hammer.<br />
2) Player(s) must be grouped/raided (if that goes live) with you to receive it.<br />
3) Once they leave the group, the prayer is nullified.<br />
4) Cleric must be within a certain range of you for prayer to stay in effect (don't know about this).<br />
5) Must be level x to have sufficient will.<br />
6) Should not be restricted to undead.<br />
7) Should not be fully resistable.<br />
8) Should be short duration (20 mins?) and have a small mana cost, short cast time.  No gem required.<br />
9) Prayer nullified if cleric is afk or botted (joke  <img src="../ubb/tongue.gif" border="0" alt="">)<br />
<br />
These suggestions are just in an effor to combat certain ways this imbue could be abused by others (as if we don't get bugged for rezzes enough, can you imagine 'prayer plz' all the time?).   One other possibility would be if a cleric of certain level is in the group, melee get an automatic proc chance on weapons, and casters get a higher chance to crit.  Just a few thoughts written down as I try to kill the last 10-15 minutes of work.  And holy ****, it worked  <img src="../ubb/smile.gif" border="0" alt="">.</font></p>
	
	<p><p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">__________________<br>
<A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=20054" TARGET="blank"><I><B>Rollie Fingrez</A></I></B><BR>57th Templar<BR>Seventh Hammer</font></p></p>
	<p></p>
