<br />
With my back turned to a mob I should take the same damage as any other plate class with the same level and ac.  It should be no contest if were both facing the mob with avoidence skills taken in to account.  Plate armor should be plate armor.<br />
<br />
I would like a short duration spell that turns a live mob into an undead mob.  That would alow our more efficient dots to be usefull.  I would gladly give this up for a few zones that were all undead.<br />
<br />
The melee mind wants buffs that they can see NOW.  "haste please" "Boon please" "DS please".  I think we need some sort of high demand short duration buff that the melee's notice when its gone.  To that end make one of the yaulp spells either a short group buff, or targetable.  <br />
<br />
I would like a AA skill that alowed me to sacrifice my self to save my MT.  Normal exp loss would occur and the corpse would be ressable.<br />
<br />
I personally don't care if I get self invis, but I would like INVIS Potions to stack.<br />
