<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" bgcolor=""  width="95%" align="center"><tr><td>
<table cellpadding="4" cellspacing="1" border="0"  width="100%">
<tr>
	<td bgcolor="#F7F7F7" width="175" valign="top" nowrap>
	<a name="post120825"></a>
	
	<font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>Laeoric</b></font><br>
	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">Cleric</font><br>
	<p>
	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">Registered: Sep 2002<br>
	Location: Innoruuk!<br>
	Posts: 16</font></td>
	
	<td bgcolor="#F7F7F7" width="100%" valign="top">
	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial"> <b></b></font>
	<p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">There isnt much that i would like to have done to the Cleric class as a whole, and many of the suggustions that i hear people talk about are unrealistic or against the class 'vision' . <br />
<br />
Honestly, i would be really happy if we were able to mitigate damage like a plate class , IE the max i get hit for is the same that the warrior gets hit for. I dont want improved dodge or block or parry - just the ability to take a hit. <br />
<br />
Also against the Undead. I would really like some new Undead only DoTs that are worth my time. Someone here posted up some good numbers on Epitaph vs. Judgement ( heck judgement isnt even an undead only nuke ). Personally i dont have any problems getting xp groups as i almost exclusively group with my guild. I dont want the ability to solo like a shaman/druid - i just want the ability to kick around a few undead while i piddle away time before a raid. <br />
<br />
I said i wouldnt like to solo, but i would like to become not as dependant upon others to go anywhere or do anything, because as we stand now - we cannot. I dont want a self invis, i dont want lev or anything of that line tho, that to me just doesnt fit into the 'clerical' image.<br />
<br />
So overall, my added suggustions would be :<br />
<br />
1. mitigate damage like a true plate class ( not by increasing skills tho, our caps are fine where they are )<br />
<br />
2. More potency in Unded-Only combat, be it via DoTs or Nukes.<br />
<br />
3. Ease back on our total dependancy on other classes to do *anything* besides raid crushbone maybe.<br />
<br />
Those are just my suggustions <img src="../ubb/smile.gif" border="0" alt=""></font></p>
	
	<p><p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">__________________<br>
Laeoric Holymight<br />
Silent Resurgence<br />
<i>Knowledge Itself is Power</i></font></p></p>
